entry.value: with aaa as ( select DATE_FORMAT(concat(a.db_date,' ',b.fulltime),'%Y-%m-%dT%H:%i:%S') as dt1,concat(a.db_date,' ',b.fulltime) as dt from time_dimension a cross join time_d b where db_date between (select DATE_FORMAT(max(PriceTimestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') as lastdate from aws.SpotPriceHistory) and DATE_FORMAT(now(),'%Y-%m-%d') ),bbb as ( select concat(a.db_date,' ',b.fulltime) as dt ,DATE_FORMAT((concat(a.db_date,' ',b.fulltime) - INTERVAL 1 HOUR),'%Y-%m-%dT%H:%i:%S') as dt2 from time_dimension a cross join time_d b where db_date between (select DATE_FORMAT(max(PriceTimestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') as lastdate from aws.SpotPriceHistory) and DATE_FORMAT(now(),'%Y-%m-%d') ) SELECT concat('ec2 describe-spot-price-history --start-time ',b.dt2,' --end-time ',a.dt1,' --region ap-southeast-2 --profile <ProfileName>') as OldDays from aaa a join bbb b on a.dt=b.dt
